<font style="font-weight: normal; font-size: small;">after <i>i</i></font></th>
<td rowspan="2"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[t]</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th><i>ch</i></th>
